Document: AudioEffect
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffect.rst
Summary: Describes the _instantiate method for creating custom AudioEffectInstance objects.

Method: _instantiate() → AudioEffectInstance
Override this method to customize the AudioEffectInstance created when this effect is applied on a bus in the editor's Audio panel, or through AudioServer.add_bus_effect(). The method must return a new AudioEffectInstance subclass instance, and it is recommended to keep a reference to the original AudioEffect in the new instance. This allows the effect instance to listen for changes at run-time and be modified accordingly.

GDScript:
    extends AudioEffect

    @export var strength = 4.0

    func _instantiate():
        var effect = CustomAudioEffectInstance.new()
        effect.base = self

        return effect

Note: It is recommended to keep a reference to the original AudioEffect in the new instance. Depending on the implementation this allows the effect instance to listen for changes at run-time and be modified accordingly.